{"comment":"<p>Creates a reusable prompt generator function.</p>\n<p>This higher-order function encapsulates common logic like token length checking,\nallowing specific prompt content generation to be handled by the provided <code>contentGenerator</code>.</p>\n<h5>Returns:</h5><p>A function that generates the full prompt string based on the input, or an empty string if it exceeds the token limit.</p>\n<h5>Example:</h5><pre><code class=\"language-ts\"><span class=\"pl-k\">const</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">myPromptGenerator</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> <span class=\"pl-en\">createPromptGenerator</span>(\n  { maxTokenLength: <span class=\"pl-c1\">10000</span> },\n  (<span class=\"pl-v\">userQuery</span><span class=\"pl-k\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">string</span>) <span class=\"pl-k\">=></span> <span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">`</span>Answer the following question: ${<span class=\"pl-smi\">userQuery</span>}<span class=\"pl-pds\">`</span></span>\n);\n<span class=\"pl-k\">const</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">prompt</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> <span class=\"pl-en\">myPromptGenerator</span>(<span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>What is the weather today?<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span>);\n<span class=\"pl-k\">if</span> (<span class=\"pl-smi\">prompt</span>) {\n  <span class=\"pl-c\">// Use the prompt with an LLM API</span>\n} <span class=\"pl-k\">else</span> {\n  <span class=\"pl-c1\">console</span>.<span class=\"pl-c1\">error</span>(<span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>Prompt was too long<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span>);\n}\n</code></pre>\n"},"sources":[{"fileName":"packages/ai-utils/src/utils/prompt/generator.ts","fullFileName":"/home/runner/work/fe-tools/fe-tools/utils/packages/ai-utils/src/utils/prompt/generator.ts","line":44,"character":0,"url":"https://github.com/MichealWayne/fe-tools/blob/3274750/utils/packages/ai-utils/src/utils/prompt/generator.ts#L44"}],"parentId":2721}],"is":{"declarati